2019年10月10日在这里举行的[[2022年國際足協世界盃外圍賽_–_亞洲區第二圈#C組|2022年國際足協世界盃外圍賽亞洲區第二圈C組]]伊朗同[[柬埔寨國家足球隊|柬埔寨]]的比赛，伊朗正式解除禁令，首次允许普通女性观众进入体育场观看足球比赛。球场开放了72个观众区的4个给女性观众，分配给她们的3,500张的很快在网上售罄<ref name="dw-191012" />，当局追加了1,100张球票<ref name="CNN-191009">{{Cite news |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/09/football/iranian-women-world-cup-qualifier-cambodia-fifa-spt-intl/index.html |title=Iranian women allowed to enter football stadium for first time in 40 years |date=2019-10-09 |work=CNN |accessdate=2019-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016163527/https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/09/football/iranian-women-world-cup-qualifier-cambodia-fifa-spt-intl/index.html |archive-date=2019-10-16 |dead-url=no |language=en}}</ref>{{noteTag|女性球迷批评伊朗当局不顾需求任意限制女性球迷入场人数，将女球迷限制在单独看台、不让她们同家人一起看球。[[伊朗原則主義派|伊朗强硬派]]则认为取消足球场女性观众禁令是在向西方势力低头。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/10/10/sports/soccer/iran-women.html |title=Iranian Women Allowed to Attend Soccer Game for First Time Since 1981 |last=Panja |first=Tariq |date=2019-10-10 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2019-11-09 |language=en-US |issn=0362-4331 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016194546/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/10/10/sports/soccer/iran-women.html |archive-date=2019-10-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}。伊朗仅取消了男足国家队世界杯预选赛的女性观众禁令，伊朗女性仍然不能入场观看伊朗国内联赛和[[亚洲冠军联赛|亚洲冠军联赛]]。<ref name="dw-191012">{{Cite news |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E8%B8%8F%E4%B8%8A%E7%94%B7%E8%B6%B3%E8%A7%82%E4%BC%97%E5%B8%AD/a-50773647 |title=伊朗女性首次踏上男足观众席 |date=2019-10-12 |work=DW |accessdate=2019-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012160436/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E8%B8%8F%E4%B8%8A%E7%94%B7%E8%B6%B3%E8%A7%82%E4%BC%97%E5%B8%AD/a-50773647 |archive-date=2019-10-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

